Ja Mong Kut.

5
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:35,000
Ja Mong Kut.

6
00:00:35,800 --> 00:00:38,000
Nemá to mať oranžovo-žltú farbu?

7
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:39,500
A má to vyzerať ako koruna.

8
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:43,000
Hovoríš o Dara Thong
alebo Thong Ake Grajung.

9
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:44,900
Sú to dezerty z Phibun-ovej éry.

10
00:00:45,800 --> 00:00:48,000
Lenže ja robím Ja Mong Kut.

11
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:50,500
Začal sa vyrábať počas vlády kráľa Rámi II.

12
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:53,000
Popravde, nemusí tam ísť ten pandánový list.

13
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:54,500
Ale páči sa mi jeho vôňa
a preto ho vždy používam.

14
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:03,320
Moja stará mama ma
zoznámila s tým dezertom.

15
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:07,800
Ale veľa si toho o ňom nepamätám.

16
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:09,000
Vždy mu dám iné meno.

17
00:01:10,990 --> 00:01:13,840
V minulosti aj
kuchárske knihy používali zlé meno.

18
00:01:15,220 --> 00:01:18,800
Tá kniha bola populárna
a rozšírená po celej krajine.

19
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,560
Na opravu mena už bolo neskoro.

20
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:26,120
A vieš aj toto?

21
00:01:26,620 --> 00:01:28,640
Ak tam dáme škoricu,

22
00:01:29,100 --> 00:01:31,000
bude to voňať ešte lepšie.

23
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:44,120
Del mi povedala,
že keď varíš,

24
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:46,920
vždy všetko robíš opatrne a pozorne.

25
00:01:46,990 --> 00:01:48,000
Má pravdu.

26
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:52,320
Krása thajských dezertov
spočíva v trpezlivosti kuchára.

27
00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:56,400
Aj keď to robíš pre zábavu,
musíš tomu venovať svoju pozornosť.

28
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:57,450
Rozumieš?

29
00:02:28,100 --> 00:02:29,360
Včera večer...

30
00:02:34,700 --> 00:02:36,000
Týka sa to Intouch-a.

31
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,000
Dean.

32
00:02:48,900 --> 00:02:49,300
Áno.

33
00:02:49,300 --> 00:02:51,300
Môžem sa ťa niečo spýtať?

34
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:56,000
Ak sa dozviem o Intouch-ovi viac,

35
00:02:57,500 --> 00:02:59,000
zmení sa náš vzťah nejak?

36
00:03:09,700 --> 00:03:10,500
Nie.

37
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:12,800
Nikdy sa nezmení.

38
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,000
Ak...

39
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,500
Ak si vypočujem jeho príbeh,

40
00:03:18,500 --> 00:03:20,120
budem z toho šťastný, či smutný?

41
00:03:22,250 --> 00:03:23,500
Asi...

42
00:03:26,300 --> 00:03:27,300
Asi budeš smutný.

43
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,000
Ak je to tak,

44
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,500
nechcem si ešte vypočuť jeho príbeh.

45
00:03:39,700 --> 00:03:40,500
Ak je to niečo smutné,

46
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:44,000
bude lepšie,
ak o tom nebudem vedieť.

47
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:45,000
Taktiež...

48
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,400
Nemôžeme zmeniť našu minulosť.

49
00:03:56,500 --> 00:03:57,500
Vieš...

50
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:02,500
Ešte nikdy som nepoužil lotosové kvety.

51
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:08,000
Ale v hlave sa mi víria určité obrazy.

52
00:04:08,500 --> 00:04:10,500
Intouch už asi držal lotosové kvety.

53
00:04:14,300 --> 00:04:16,300
Možno budem občas pociťovať smútok,

54
00:04:16,899 --> 00:04:20,999
no je podľa mňa správne
nechať minulosť minulosťou.

55
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:23,400
Ozaj.

56
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:26,700
Je jedna pieseň,
ktorá má krásny text.

57
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,400
“Ak sa mi vrátia spomienky z minulosti,”

58
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:33,500
“chcem spomínať iba na krásne veci.”

59
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:36,700
“Chcem totiž vkročiť do krásneho zajtrajška.”

60
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:40,500
Moja mama tú pieseň miluje.

61
00:04:41,500 --> 00:04:42,500
Má krásny význam.

62
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,500
Prečo sa mračíš?

63
00:05:10,300 --> 00:05:11,300
Vzdávam sa.

64
00:05:15,300 --> 00:05:17,000
Vzdávaš sa?

65
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:21,000
Vzdávam sa.

66
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:26,000
Som do teba po uši zamilovaný.

67
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,500
Môžem ťa pobozkať?

68
00:05:35,700 --> 00:05:37,000
Pobozkám ťa.

69
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:56,300
Dean.

70
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,500
Dean.

71
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,000
Dean.

72
00:06:09,500 --> 00:06:10,500
Parm.

73
00:06:13,300 --> 00:06:14,000
Prepáč.

74
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,000
Otvor ústa.

75
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,500
No tak.

76
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:04,200
Chutí to dobre?

77
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:10,500
Už niečo také nikdy neurob, dobre?

78
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,000
Dobre.

79
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,560
Už niečo také nikdy neurobím.

80
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:50,000
Team.

81
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,600
Ráno som volala Parm-ovi.

82
00:07:51,700 --> 00:07:54,000
A?

83
00:07:58,500 --> 00:07:59,500
Čo?

84
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:07,500
Čo je s ním?

85
00:08:11,300 --> 00:08:12,500
Čo je s Parm-om?

86
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:17,500
Dobre ma počúvaj.

87
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,000
Dean.

88
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:19,500
Zdvihol.

89
00:08:19,500 --> 00:08:19,800
Parm-ov.

90
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,000
Krásny.

91
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:20,800
Mobil.

92
00:08:24,500 --> 00:08:25,500
Som si istá.

93
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,000
Konečne!

94
00:08:35,500 --> 00:08:37,300
Čo je to s tebou?
Mal by si byť šťastný.

95
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:40,000
Smrdí ti z úst.

96
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,000
Prepáč.

97
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:45,300
Som si istá.

98
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:49,500
Si v poriadku?

99
00:08:50,700 --> 00:08:51,600
To je Parm?

100
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:54,000
Ja neviem.
Otvor dvere.

101
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:55,700
Musím sa upokojiť.

102
00:08:59,000 --> 00:08:59,500
Ty...

103
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:01,000
Poď sem.

104
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,000
Poď.

105
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,000
Rýchlo.

106
00:09:11,300 --> 00:09:12,300
Čo?

107
00:09:13,500 --> 00:09:15,300
Priznaj sa.

108
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,000
Čože?

109
00:09:22,300 --> 00:09:24,500
Povedz nám,
prečo Dean zdvihol tvoj mobil.

110
00:09:25,700 --> 00:09:26,700
A bolo to skoro ráno.

111
00:09:27,500 --> 00:09:29,500
Chceš mi povedať,
že u teba nespal?

112
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:38,000
Nie je to predsa normálne?

113
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:39,700
Manaow.

114
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,700
Normálne...

115
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:46,300
Nič by som nepovedala,
keby ste boli iba kamaráti.

116
00:09:46,300 --> 00:09:47,000
Lenže vy spolu...

117
00:09:47,500 --> 00:09:48,500
Čo?

118
00:09:48,500 --> 00:09:49,500
Manaow.

119
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,000
Preboha!

120
00:09:57,500 --> 00:09:58,500
Čo chceš?

121
00:10:00,500 --> 00:10:02,000
Nepovedz mi,

122
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,500
že ťa už stihol "zjesť".

123
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,500
Zjesť?

124
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:08,000
Určite.

125
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:09,500
Ukáž sa.

126
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:10,500
Prestaňte.

127
00:10:10,500 --> 00:10:11,000
Musím sa o tom presvedčiť.

128
00:10:11,500 --> 00:10:13,000
Nedám vám žiadne dezerty.

129
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:16,000
No tak.

130
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:16,500
Daj mi to.

131
00:10:16,500 --> 00:10:18,500
Už si jedol,
tak m to daj.

132
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:19,300
Nejedol som.

133
00:10:19,300 --> 00:10:20,000
Jedol si.

134
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:21,200
Vidím to na tebe.

135
00:10:23,500 --> 00:10:24,700
Vy...

136
00:10:24,700 --> 00:10:26,500
Dozviem sa pravdu!
Dám ti do izby kameru!

137
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,700
Kameru?

138
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:29,700
Čo je to?

139
00:10:39,500 --> 00:10:41,000
Čo robíš?

140
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:43,000
Čítam knihu.
Prestaň.

141
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,000
Akú knihu?

142
00:10:52,500 --> 00:10:54,000
Nepoviem ti.

143
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:56,000
Ahoj, Dean.

144
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:02,000
Prečo si nám nepovedal,
že budeš spať u Parm-a?

145
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:05,300
Prepáč.

146
00:11:05,300 --> 00:11:07,000
Bolo už neskoro.

147
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,500
Niečo pod zub.

148
00:11:09,500 --> 00:11:10,500
Ďakujem.

149
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:18,000
Čím je to obalené?
Je to roztomilé.

150
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,500
Parm povedal,
že sú to lotosové kvety.

151
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:25,000
Čo je to za dezert?
Nikdy predtým som ho nevidela.

152
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:27,500
Ja Mong Kut.

153
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,500
Nemá to mať oranžovo-žltú farbu?

154
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:35,000
Spýtaj sa na to Parm-a.

155
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:38,000
Don, pozri sa.

156
00:11:40,500 --> 00:11:41,800
Môžeme to len tak zjesť?

157
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:43,800
Nie, musíš to odbaliť.

158
00:11:46,500 --> 00:11:47,500
Je to roztomilé.

159
00:11:53,700 --> 00:11:55,700
Kedy sa vrátia rodičia?

160
00:11:56,700 --> 00:11:59,000
Na konci roka,
alebo začiatkom nového roka.

161
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,500
Už si hľadajú letenky.

162
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,000
Ale...

163
00:12:02,500 --> 00:12:05,000
Neviem, či sa stihnú
vrátiť do tvojich pretekov.

164
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:25,500
Vy dvaja....

165
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:27,500
Už ste niekedy boli u starej mamy?

166
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,500
Ty...

167
00:12:34,500 --> 00:12:36,000
Myslel som si,
že ju nemáš rád.

168
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,500
O čom to hovoríš?

169
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:41,200
Kto niečo také povedal?

170
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:44,500
No...

171
00:12:44,500 --> 00:12:46,500
Otec povedal,

172
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:49,000
že jeho mama nemala rada našu mamu.

173
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:51,000
Nemala rada rodinu z maminej strany.

174
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:54,500
Preto sme si mysleli...

175
00:12:55,500 --> 00:12:58,000
K nenávisti som nebol vychovaný.

176
00:12:58,500 --> 00:12:59,500
Takže...

177
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,500
Už ste sa s ňou niekedy stretli?

178
00:13:02,550 --> 00:13:05,700
Chodíme za ňou často,
ale nepovedali sme ti to.

179
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,000
My...

180
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:10,000
Báli sme sa,
že sa nahneváš.

181
00:13:10,500 --> 00:13:11,000
Ale...

182
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:14,000
Naša stará mama sa stále po tebe pýta.

183
00:13:14,500 --> 00:13:16,500
Vždy jej ukazujem tvoje fotky.

184
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:22,500
Chcem sa s ňou stretnúť.

185
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,500
Chcem sa stretnúť s našou starou mamou.

186
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:28,500
Dúfam, že to bude dnes.

187
00:13:29,500 --> 00:13:31,000
Zoberiete ma k nej?

188
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:33,000
Tak...

189
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:37,000
Počkaj.

190
00:13:49,500 --> 00:13:50,500
Haló?

191
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,000
Áno.

192
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:54,500
Si doma?

193
00:13:55,700 --> 00:13:57,500
Dobre.

194
00:13:58,000 --> 00:14:00,500
Dnes za tebou prídeme.

195
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:03,000
Dobre.

196
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:04,000
Rozumiem.

197
00:14:04,600 --> 00:14:05,600
Uvidíme sa neskôr.

198
00:14:07,300 --> 00:14:08,000
Je doma.

199
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:11,000
Nebýva ďaleko.

200
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:12,000
Takže...

201
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:13,000
Pôjdeme?

